74
00:05:36,517 --> 00:05:40,578
is not only extracting elements from real life,

75
00:05:40,578 --> 00:05:44,419
but some special designs are also affecting

76
00:05:44,419 --> 00:05:47,080
the public aesthetics.

77
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:51,141
In 2000s, when Audition Online was the most popular game

78
