109
00:08:27,209 --> 00:08:28,631
and the curly hair.

110
00:08:29,828 --> 00:08:32,230
The examples go on and on.

111
00:08:32,230 --> 00:08:36,833
From above, we can easily feel that whether it's

112
00:08:36,833 --> 00:08:39,796
Eastern or Western, the design of hairstyle

