149
00:11:46,934 --> 00:11:49,396
and the gameplay in the game are different.

150
00:11:49,396 --> 00:11:54,178
So what is the aesthetics difference

151
00:11:54,178 --> 00:11:57,179
between Eastern and Western hairstyles?

152
00:11:57,179 --> 00:12:00,761
Before showing the case, please allow

153
00:12:00,761 --> 00:12:03,702
me to extend some Eastern and Western differences

154
00:12:03,702 --> 00:12:05,003
in traditional painting.

155
00:12:06,841 --> 00:12:10,382
I believe that everyone who has visited

156
00:12:10,382 --> 00:12:11,983
a Western classical painting

157
00:12:11,983 --> 00:12:14,684
and an ancient Chinese painting in a museum

158
00:12:14,684 --> 00:12:19,606
will find that there are great differences between them two.

159
00:12:19,606 --> 00:12:22,528
It's two completely different systems.

160
00:12:23,763 --> 00:12:27,866
Relatively speaking, Western classical painting

161
00:12:27,866 --> 00:12:30,347
focus on lighting and shadow,

162
00:12:30,347 --> 00:12:33,549
perspective and anatomical structure,

163
00:12:33,549 --> 00:12:38,492
which tend to present the reality in painting.

164
00:12:38,492 --> 00:12:41,134
Whether figures or landscapes,

165
00:12:41,134 --> 00:12:43,415
Western classical painting express

166
00:12:43,415 --> 00:12:45,676
the material world and the reality.

167
00:12:46,551 --> 00:12:52,374
So to speak, Western aesthetics mainly focus on creating,

168
00:12:52,374 --> 00:12:56,696
recreating and attaches great importance to realism.

169
00:12:56,696 --> 00:13:03,100
In contrast, the Eastern ancient painting

170
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:07,042
are not more about describing the real world,

171
00:13:07,042 --> 00:13:11,384
but a kind of expression of personal feelings.

172
00:13:11,384 --> 00:13:14,006
Take ancient Chinese painting as an example.

173
00:13:15,108 --> 00:13:17,409
This is a part of China's national treasure,

174
00:13:17,409 --> 00:13:21,911
a thousand miles of rivers and mountains

175
00:13:21,911 --> 00:13:25,472
from Northern Song dynasty more than a thousand years ago.

176
00:13:25,472 --> 00:13:31,915
When we feel the beauty of the, we can feel the beauty of the landscape

177
00:13:31,915 --> 00:13:35,596
from painting, but the landscape are completely

178
00:13:35,596 --> 00:13:40,719
inconsistent with light and shadow, perspective and structure.

179
00:13:40,719 --> 00:13:44,720
This is the most important point of Chinese painting.

180
00:13:45,377 --> 00:13:46,598
Feeling expression.

181
00:13:46,598 --> 00:13:50,499
Realism is neither needed nor value

182
00:13:50,499 --> 00:13:52,819
in Chinese traditional painting.

183
00:13:52,819 --> 00:13:56,400
In fact, you can't find such a mountain like that at all.

184
00:13:56,400 --> 00:14:00,521
And this blue color on the top of mountain

185
00:14:00,521 --> 00:14:03,562
is also impossible in natural reality.

186
00:14:03,562 --> 00:14:06,743
But we can still feel the same feeling

187
00:14:06,743 --> 00:14:10,124
as when the author painting.

188
00:14:10,124 --> 00:14:10,924
That is beauty.

189
00:14:11,693 --> 00:14:15,556
Due to this difference in Eastern and Western aesthetics,

190
00:14:15,556 --> 00:14:20,359
the difference between reproducing reality

191
00:14:20,359 --> 00:14:25,183
and the expression emotions, the difference in hair design

192
00:14:25,183 --> 00:14:27,945
aesthetics is caused.

193
00:14:27,945 --> 00:14:31,107
And it is also the difference in players' acceptance

194
00:14:31,107 --> 00:14:34,890
of hair aesthetics between Eastern and Western-themed

195
00:14:34,890 --> 00:14:35,190
games.

196
00:14:37,208 --> 00:14:41,855
Therefore, Western themed games focus on realism,

197
00:14:41,855 --> 00:14:44,298
restore the shape in real life,

198
00:14:44,298 --> 00:14:48,144
and pay more attention to the sense of reality,

199
00:14:48,144 --> 00:14:50,908
such as the main character's hairstyle changing

200
00:14:50,908 --> 00:14:52,791
during the fighting process.

201
00:14:53,387 --> 00:15:00,351
Taking Last of Us 2 as an example, the shape of the hair is consistent with reality.

202
00:15:00,351 --> 00:15:08,035
The hair roots are distinct. The material is very realistic. The surrounding broken hair is

203
00:15:08,035 --> 00:15:12,998
clearly shown. And some shorter hair are struggled after the battle,

204
00:15:12,998 --> 00:15:17,480
which is very realistic and physically true.

205
00:15:18,973 --> 00:15:25,097
When seeing this, players will price the sense of reality.

206
00:15:25,097 --> 00:15:28,638
On the other hand, many Oriental-themed games

207
00:15:28,638 --> 00:15:33,061
consider the styling and the production of hair

208
00:15:33,061 --> 00:15:36,983
from another direction, and will pay more attention

209
00:15:36,983 --> 00:15:41,305
to the silhouette, outline, and the beauty of the styling,

210
00:15:41,305 --> 00:15:45,947
while sacrificing part of the realism and the rationality.

211
00:15:48,275 --> 00:15:56,979
Take three Chinese style games produced by our NetEase Thunderfire Studio, for example.

212
00:15:56,979 --> 00:16:04,503
They are Justice Online, Narca Blade Point, Wangchuan Fenghua Lu.

213
00:16:04,503 --> 00:16:12,847
So whether it is a realistic art style or a two-dimensional art style game,

214
00:16:14,489 --> 00:16:17,070
The hair design tended to pay more attention

215
00:16:17,070 --> 00:16:20,391
to the beauty of the silhouette, shape, and the line,

216
00:16:20,391 --> 00:16:25,253
sacrificing part of the realistic feel.

217
00:16:25,253 --> 00:16:29,274
In Justice Online, on the left, her hairstyle

218
00:16:29,274 --> 00:16:33,395
