00:17:48,618 --> 00:17:50,458
Therefore, in those projects,

239
00:17:51,732 --> 00:18:05,209
Artists make a choice, giving up part of the reality of haircuts when we designing and producing hair, which is different from the realistic style in Western game.

240
00:18:05,209 --> 00:18:07,632
After brief.

241
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:15,288
After briefly talking about the similarities and the differences mentioned above,

242
00:18:15,288 --> 00:18:19,873
let me introduce how we design Oriental hairstyles.

243
00:18:19,873 --> 00:18:28,543
As mentioned earlier, both Eastern and Western games have one thing in common in terms of aesthetics.

244
00:18:29,519 --> 00:18:36,926
