247
00:18:49,398 --> 00:18:51,400
So how do we find elements?

248
00:18:52,473 --> 00:18:54,975
This goes back to Chinese painting.

249
00:18:54,975 --> 00:18:58,538
We pick the specific elements from historical painting

250
00:18:58,538 --> 00:19:00,860
and then recreate to our works.

251
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:04,203
The traditional Chinese ink painting

252
00:19:04,203 --> 00:19:06,805
is formed by one stroke.

253
00:19:06,805 --> 00:19:09,448
Due to the characteristic of the brush,

254
00:19:09,448 --> 00:19:13,411
there will be different thickness changes in one stroke.

